cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SD 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine translation, specifically in the context of sarcasm interpretation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses machine learning algorithms and evaluation measures, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with sentiment analysis, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing).
